properties.headline: FLOODING - THE UNINCORPORATED AREA OF THE WESTERN REGION various roads
properties.otherAdvice:
• All highways in the region are open (Barrier Highway and Silver City Highway).
  • Mutawintji Rd is open with caution to 4 wheel drives only due to rain, between Mutawintji National Park and White Cliffs.
  • A number of local roads are also affected by flooding.

A complete listing of roads is recorded on 08 8082 6660.
